import reactJS from '../imgs/reactJS.png'

  return(
    
    <>
     <Grid container spacing={2}>

      <Grid item>

      />

      <Grid item >
        <HomeCard />
      </Grid>
      <Grid item >
        <HomeCard />
      </Grid>
    </Grid>
    </>

    
  )
}

export default Home
